</style><h3 id="outline__1_2" class="wp-block-heading">参考记录（最大的当地办事处/集团等）</h3><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>办公室/团体名称——</strong><br>所属团体名称等<br><br></td><td><strong>附属频道</strong><br>——<br>通道数<br>（增加减少）</td><td><strong>平均注册人数——</strong><br>注册总人数<br>（较1周前有变化）</td></tr><tr><td><strong>算法项目</strong><br>（实际生产）<br> ——<br>・人才频道 ・官方频道<br><br></td><td><strong>29</strong><br> ——<br> 30<br> ├29<br> └1<br> (±0)</td><td> <strong>53,342 人</strong>（+491 人）<br> （1,546,930 人中）<br> 1,675,930人├1,546,930人└129,000人（+14,240人）▼</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> *显然是泰国最大的办公室</figcaption></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__1_3" class="wp-block-heading">人才/机构/团体信息</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="lcsyYlYpI7"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/brave-group-european-vtuber-agency-globie-debuts-1st-gen-talent-pippa-pebblesworth-in-early-december/">Brave集团欧洲VTuber办公室全球1代《Pippa Pebblesworth》12月初登场</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Brave Group欧洲VTuber经纪公司globie 1代“Pippa Pebblesworth”12月初出道” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/brave-group-european-vtuber-agency-globie-debuts-1st-gen-talent-pippa-pebblesworth-in-early-december/embed/#?secret=aNzNQC6jYB#?secret=lcsyYlYpI7" data-secret="lcsyYlYpI7" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="NVNrF3NfFX"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/haconect-vtuber-ayasaka-kiho-suspended-due-to-confirmation-of-contract-violation/">HaConnect所属VTuber绫坂喜步因确认违反合同而暂停活动</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security=